dct_title_s: Railroad commissioners' map of Minnesota corrected to Sept. 1, 1904

dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:633,600]. Also shows congressional districts. "Ira B. Mills, Joseph G. Miller, C.F. Staples, Railroad and Warehouse Commissioners; A.C. Clausen, Secretary." Insets: Vicinity of Duluth & Superior, Wis. Scale [1:506,880] -- Vicinity of Saint Paul & Minneapolis. Scale [1:316,800] -- Mesaba Range. Scale [1:506,880] -- Cook County. Scale [1:663,600]. Index on verso. Index on verso obscured by cloth backing. Dimensions: 120 x 75 centimeters
